{"tid":2080094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"電訊盈科入稟高等法院控告政府","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T05:51:23.000Z","uid":5195,"like":727,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"73b8bc986ebfde6aba9ec9ff04a94277d2c2b406","tid":2080094,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:02:13.000Z","msg":"電訊盈科入稟高等法院控告政府，指早年雙方簽訂合約，電盈為社署的長者生活津貼及「廣東計劃」提供電腦系統服務，惟政府單方面非法中止合約，違反協議，遂興訟要求政府賠償合約款項逾港幣3.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n原告電訊盈科企業方案有限公司，控告律政司司長。入稟狀透露，原告於2011年8月25日與政府物流服務署簽訂協議，為社署社會保障電腦系統提供服務，涉及長者生活津貼及「廣東計劃」，有關系統的建設和維修費用為港幣3.56億元。但是，政府於2014年6月27日單方面非法終止合約。原告現要求法庭聲明政府非法中止協議和毀約，除追討合約涉款外，另要求政府補償原告就該合約所衍生的開支等。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA1046/20】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/S7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FS7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=653c9066\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FS7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q%2F&h=9215ac67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/S7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"7b7107c2a29f1084a8d319c6e9896ef917252ce1","tid":2080094,"uid":8014,"like":491,"dislike":1,"score":490,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"咁大膽告政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試圖顛覆國家政權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6f1763ca5aad149d2c53b5421d267e6eee8906","tid":2080094,"uid":256019,"like":359,"dislike":0,"score":359,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"有乜好而家告晒喇！遲d国安法通過後，你再告就係破壞国家安全，李澤楷會被国安拉上支那秘密審訊，最高刑罰係死刑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd5ce183ee267258b80c1e2b911db9847789b35","tid":2080094,"uid":51057,"li