08:02:13.000Z","msg":"電訊盈科入稟高等法院控告政府，指早年雙方簽訂合約，電盈為社署的長者生活津貼及「廣東計劃」提供電腦系統服務，惟政府單方面非法中止合約，違反協議，遂興訟要求政府賠償合約款項逾港幣3.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n原告電訊盈科企業方案有限公司，控告律政司司長。入稟狀透露，原告於2011年8月25日與政府物流服務署簽訂協議，為社署社會保障電腦系統提供服務，涉及長者生活津貼及「廣東計劃」，有關系統的建設和維修費用為港幣3.56億元。但是，政府於2014年6月27日單方面非法終止合約。原告現要求法庭聲明政府非法中止協議和毀約，除追討合約涉款外，另要求政府補償原告就該合約所衍生的開支等。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA1046/20】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/S7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FS7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=653c9066\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200626%2FS7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q%2F&h=9215ac67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200626/S7UKJRYFQ2QKJZ447YHVUZRV4Q/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩鳩返港共，吹咩"},{"pid":"174e862dba79417ba95fea078ecec4100e75e96d","tid":2080094,"uid":146737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=e60fe0fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"90c6aeb508872a1eb80b2f2730394c61446fef26","tid":2080094,"uid":157532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1d68ceb702ea5071a0842d3d9b67b807ab30dd","tid":2080094,"uid":45082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140712/mobile/odn-20140712-0712_00176_082.html\" data-s